OOC: I'll never forget you Logo.  Good luck in what ever you do, because i 
know you'll succeed.

:::Starscream/Battera:::

::He almost smiles when she says she'll go back with him, but holds it back 
when she mentions old leaders::
Starscream: Old leaders?
Battera: I-i dont want to talk about it.
::Starscream is frowning. This girl obviously has had a bad life::
Starscream: Okay.
::He transforms to vehicle mode::
Starscream: Hop in.
::Battera gets in and Starscream takes off, headed for the Blackfortress::

--part1_3e.97d1163.27f486a3_boundary
